<a name="details" id="details"></a><h2 class="groupheader">Detailed Description</h2>
<div class="textblock"><p>This class wraps an HTTP request, which is basically : </p>
<ul>
<li>a header with a method, a target URI, and a set of field/value pairs</li>
<li>an optional body (for POST requests) </li>
</ul>

